README.md
     1→# NeverThrow 🙅
     2→
     3→[![GitHub Workflow Status](https://github.com/supermacro/neverthrow/actions/workflows/ci.yml/badge.svg?branch=master)](https://github.com/supermacro/neverthrow/actions)
     5→## Description
     6→
     7→Encode failure into your program.
